description:
There are two necessary ingredients to have a vibrant, healing salvation experience in Christ. Repentance and faith are both essential for mental and spiritual wellness. What is repentance? What does it mean? Dan Gabbert opens Gods Word to focus on Gods gift of repentance and how it can transform our Christian experience.

Many dont understand what repentance is or how to experience it. But it is Gods gift of repentance that enables us to think differently so we can change our responses to the things that trouble us. Without repentance, we cannot experience the healing of our mental and spiritual health.

Discover Gods amazing gift of repentance, an essential element in mental and spiritual wellbeing.
